OL,3,CTributes paid as Benidorm star dies
OL,4,Caged 89
OL,6,FTributes have been paid to Benidorm
OL,7,Fstar Elsie Kelly who has died aged 89
OL,8,Fafter a short illness.
OL,10,FElsie, from Bootle in Merseyside, had
OL,11,Fa career spanning more than five
OL,12,Fdecades appearing in Crossroads, The
OL,13,FFamous Five and Harry and the
OL,14,FWrinklies.
OL,16,FBut she was most well-known for her
OL,17,Frole as Noreen Maltby in the hit
OL,18,Fcomedy show Benidorm, appearing in the
OL,19,Fshow from 2007 until 2012, before
OL,20,Freprising the character between 2015
OL,21,Fand 2018.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
