OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776953471
OL,3,CTributes paid as Benidorm star dies
OL,4,Caged 89
OL,6,FConfirming her death, her agent,
OL,7,FMichelle Sykes, said the actress had
OL,8,Fbeen unwell for a short time.
OL,10,FIn a statement, she said: "She passed
OL,11,Faway peacefully, after a short
OL,12,Fillness, surrounded by her loving
OL,13,Ffamily on 21 April 2026 at the age of
OL,14,F89.
OL,16,F"With a career spanning decades across
OL,17,Ftelevision, theatre, and film, she
OL,18,Fmost recently became a household name
OL,19,Fthrough her work on Benidorm...
OL,26,@rD@[OUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776953471
OL,3,CTributes paid as Benidorm star dies
OL,4,Caged 89
OL,6,F"Her unmistakable charm, sharp timing
OL,7,Fand gentle humour made her a fan
OL,8,Ffavourite.
OL,10,F"Beyond this iconic role, she appeared
OL,11,Fin numerous British television
OL,12,Fprogrammes, including Inside No. 9,
OL,13,FHarry & the Wrinklies, The Famous Five
OL,14,Fand Crossroads."
OL,16,FTributes have flooded in for the
OL,17,Factress, including from former
OL,18,FBenidorm co-star Johnny Vegas, who
OL,19,Fcalled the performer a "mother figure"
OL,20,Fwho made "going into work a pure joy".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
