PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776953471
OL,3,CTributes paid as Benidorm star dies
OL,4,Caged 89
OL,6,F"A more generous, talented, funny,
OL,7,Fkind and hard grafting soul as an
OL,8,Factor you could ever hope to meet," he
OL,9,Fwrote in a post on Instagram.
OL,11,F"Elsie was a Mother figure to me, on
OL,12,Fand off screen, and guided me through
OL,13,Fmany highs and lows whilst overseas
OL,14,Ftogether.
OL,16,F"When I say Elsie was loved by all, it
OL,17,Fis a wonderful fact, not merely an apt
OL,18,Fcomment to make during such sad times.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776953471
OL,3,CTributes paid as Benidorm star dies
OL,4,Caged 89
OL,6,F"I had many young actors over the
OL,7,Fyears saying to me 'I worked with your
OL,8,FMum,' Elsie touched and guided so many
OL,9,Fcareers and crammed more into her 89
OL,10,Fyears than anyone else I've known in
OL,11,Fthis profession.
OL,13,F"When not giggling poolside, she was
OL,14,Fin her hotel room, putting together
OL,15,Fher next musical line-up for many a
OL,16,FLiverpool theatrical production.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776953471
OL,3,CTributes paid as Benidorm star dies
OL,4,Caged 89
OL,6,F"Elsie made going into work a true
OL,7,Fjoy, in fact, it was more like
OL,8,Fplaytime, and our time together,
OL,9,Fsomething to truly treasure. Bless you
OL,10,Fmy other Mum, and thank you for the
OL,11,Fendless joy you brought into so many
OL,12,Fof our lives."
OL,14,FFellow Benidorm actress Crissy Rock,
OL,15,Falso shared her sadness online. She
OL,16,Fwrote: "So sad to hear of the passing
OL,17,Fof Elsie Kelly this morning.
OL,19,F"We shared so many wonderful memories
OL,20,Ffilming Benidorm, moments I'll always
OL,21,Ftreasure."
OL,26,@xD@HOU{D@AOU
